  "948": {
    "inputs": {
      "global_prompt": "Epic cinematic fantasy adventure in a rainy neon Asian megacity at night, starring a brave orange tabby cat hero wearing a weathered brown explorer cloak, small utility harness, and backpack. A majestic blue luminous dragon spirit appears above the city and becomes the cat’s companion. Hyperrealistic cinematic digital art, dramatic shadows, strong rim light, wet reflective streets, neon cyan and crimson glow, deep charcoal atmosphere, mist, rain, volumetric lighting, dynamic camera movement, emotional heroic mood, high detail, vertical 9:16, no text, no subtitles, no logo, no watermark.",
      "max_frames": 674,
      "timeline_data": "{\"segments\":[{\"prompt\":\"The brave orange tabby cat hero stands on the edge of a high rooftop, looking over a vast rainy neon Asian megacity. Its brown explorer cloak flutters in the wind, rain falls across the frame, and the wet rooftop reflects blue and crimson city lights. In the storm clouds above the skyline, a faint glowing dragon-shaped silhouette slowly forms from mist and lightning. The camera starts behind the cat and performs a slow cinematic push-in toward the city and the dragon cloud. The cat stays still, ears alert, filled with wonder and courage. Maintain the same cat design, cloak, harness, rainy cyberpunk fantasy city, blue dragon glow, dramatic rim light, hyperrealistic cinematic style. No text, no subtitles.\",\"length\":204,\"color\":\"#4f8edc\"},{\"prompt\":\"The scene cuts to street level in the same rainy neon city. The orange tabby cat hero walks slowly through a wet reflective alley, cloak dragging and fluttering in the rain. Ahead, the blue luminous dragon spirit descends from the storm clouds and coils between the tall buildings, glowing through mist and rain. Neon signs and warm lanterns reflect on the pavement. The cat stops and looks up at the dragon in awe, but does not run away. The camera tracks behind the cat, then tilts upward to reveal the dragon’s massive glowing face. Keep the same character, same cloak and harness, same blue spectral dragon, same cinematic fantasy cyberpunk atmosphere. No text, no subtitles.\",\"length\":192,\"color\":\"#e07b3a\"},{\"prompt\":\"The blue luminous dragon lowers its head toward the orange tabby cat hero, inviting the cat to climb on. The cat leaps bravely onto the dragon’s glowing crystalline scales, gripping firmly with its paws as the cloak whips in the wind. The dragon rises from the rainy street, lifting the cat above the neon buildings. Blue energy trails spiral around them, rain streaks past the camera, and the city lights become smaller below. The camera circles slightly around the dragon and cat as they take off, creating a powerful heroic transformation moment. Maintain visual continuity with the same cat, same dragon, same city, same lighting and color palette. No text, no subtitles.\",\"length\":156,\"color\":\"#5cb85c\"},{\"prompt\":\"The orange tabby cat hero rides on the back of the glowing blue dragon as they soar through the stormy sky above the futuristic neon city. The dragon flies fast between clouds and skyscrapers, leaving bright blue energy trails behind. The cat crouches forward with a focused heroic expression, cloak streaming dramatically in the wind. Below, the city glows with crimson traffic lights, cyan neon towers, and deep charcoal shadows. The camera follows beside them in a smooth dynamic tracking shot, then slowly pulls wider to show the scale of the dragon above the city. Epic fantasy action, high speed but smooth motion, cinematic lighting, rain, mist, no text, no subtitles.\",\"length\":121,\"color\":\"#d9534f\"}]}",
      "local_prompts": "The brave orange tabby cat hero stands on the edge of a high rooftop, looking over a vast rainy neon Asian megacity. Its brown explorer cloak flutters in the wind, rain falls across the frame, and the wet rooftop reflects blue and crimson city lights. In the storm clouds above the skyline, a faint glowing dragon-shaped silhouette slowly forms from mist and lightning. The camera starts behind the cat and performs a slow cinematic push-in toward the city and the dragon cloud. The cat stays still, ears alert, filled with wonder and courage. Maintain the same cat design, cloak, harness, rainy cyberpunk fantasy city, blue dragon glow, dramatic rim light, hyperrealistic cinematic style. No text, no subtitles. | The scene cuts to street level in the same rainy neon city. The orange tabby cat hero walks slowly through a wet reflective alley, cloak dragging and fluttering in the rain. Ahead, the blue luminous dragon spirit descends from the storm clouds and coils between the tall buildings, glowing through mist and rain. Neon signs and warm lanterns reflect on the pavement. The cat stops and looks up at the dragon in awe, but does not run away. The camera tracks behind the cat, then tilts upward to reveal the dragon’s massive glowing face. Keep the same character, same cloak and harness, same blue spectral dragon, same cinematic fantasy cyberpunk atmosphere. No text, no subtitles. | The blue luminous dragon lowers its head toward the orange tabby cat hero, inviting the cat to climb on. The cat leaps bravely onto the dragon’s glowing crystalline scales, gripping firmly with its paws as the cloak whips in the wind. The dragon rises from the rainy street, lifting the cat above the neon buildings. Blue energy trails spiral around them, rain streaks past the camera, and the city lights become smaller below. The camera circles slightly around the dragon and cat as they take off, creating a powerful heroic transformation moment. Maintain visual continuity with the same cat, same dragon, same city, same lighting and color palette. No text, no subtitles. | The orange tabby cat hero rides on the back of the glowing blue dragon as they soar through the stormy sky above the futuristic neon city. The dragon flies fast between clouds and skyscrapers, leaving bright blue energy trails behind. The cat crouches forward with a focused heroic expression, cloak streaming dramatically in the wind. Below, the city glows with crimson traffic lights, cyan neon towers, and deep charcoal shadows. The camera follows beside them in a smooth dynamic tracking shot, then slowly pulls wider to show the scale of the dragon above the city. Epic fantasy action, high speed but smooth motion, cinematic lighting, rain, mist, no text, no subtitles.",
      "segment_lengths": "204, 192, 156, 121",
